Definition: plant bearing very small and very hot oblong red fruits
Example: includes wild forms native to tropical America; thought to be ancestral to the sweet pepper and many hot peppers
Synonyms: Capsicum_frutescens_baccatum, Capsicum_baccatum, pepper, genus_Capsicum, m, plant, bearing, very, small, and, hot, oblong, red, fruits, includes, wild, forms, native, to, tropical, America, thought, be, ancestral, the, sweet, many, peppers
Category: noun.plant
